Di logue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Takasu here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji got sick and was hospitalized right before New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still at home sick right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't that serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should go and visit him later{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.60,0:00:44.06,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)\fs66\pos(400,520.5)}Always, Like This
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up sleeping through the whole winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I face her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was rejected... wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why did you close it again all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here! Hey, Tai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The noodles are soggy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating junk food again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're so annoying, I'll eat it right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've cooked for you every single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you come over since New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad at me just because Minorin rejected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I want you to pity me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just treat me like you usually do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this for the sake of you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd support Minorin, but I always just crash at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for her to misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think that's why she rejected me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she just doesn't feel that w{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think Minorin likes you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she probably thinks I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Do you really think Minorin doesn't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling she's kind of interested in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't come over anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to wake me up every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still feel the same about Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should do what you should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away from Minorin! You have to confirm her true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't burn down your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I promise I won't use the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby declare I'll only eat fast food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I wonder how long you'll last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll last, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even stamped it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stamped?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Okinawa thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really going to Okinawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for me to care about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see Kushieda, the first thing I'll do is greet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to return this to you as soon as possible since it looked really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I traded you{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this was in the pocket the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't end up needing it that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea! The sun! Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herbal wine! Chinsuko! Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six days and five nights in Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. Where's Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga! Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Penis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga is going to bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were bothering me with your Chinsuko crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it look on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is still Ryuuji's!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.21,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you guys are all hyped up for the new semester!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-G{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish everything would just burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the field trip won't be canceled,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go as planned, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I don't understand what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel we were going to stay at in Okinawa burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field trip will now be a ski trip for three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I burned the hotel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Objection! This is nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why is Ami-chan late today of all days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ami-chan were here, she'd definitely have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima-san was modeling in Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's couldn't make it back for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since she's already spent a lot of time in the southern islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd probably want to go to a snowy mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:38.43,Chalk2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(400,0)}Not everything goes smoothly in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Taiga said she had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I'll try my best by myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}If you still feel the same about Minorin,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's even living on cup noodles for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be working in Hawaii?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be picking a fight when we haven't even seen each other recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you because you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.21,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to meet ten minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so picky, stupid chi'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is what you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys are already friendly enough to exchange gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I paid for it, so it's not actually a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is useless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just wear it when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to take it with you to Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field trip is now a ski trip for three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said the hotel in Okinawa burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.13,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you before the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, don't hang around Ryuuji during the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd bother {\i1}me{\i0} to hang around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Ryuuji was rejected by Minorin on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it was right before I was going to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She rejected me by hinting that I shouldn't confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Minorin likes Ryuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for some reason, things aren't moving along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have exams once we're seniors, and we'll be in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This field trip is his last chance to confirm Minorin's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that, stupid chi'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with it if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a boring conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully you're the {\i1}only{\i0} one getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as stupid as you could never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you following me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd go that far for Kushieda and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... So... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps confirming Kushieda's feelings would be a waste of effort, but{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! You and Minorin like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Where did you get all that confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reason to believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're capable of becoming Minorin's lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a new convenience store there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that attitude today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't move forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Mornin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... About yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't even on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm going first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take care of this since you got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Taiga, damn that Taiga, damn that{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm totally all right with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let me hold a side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, your hair looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut the front a bit shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wanted to cut it so short that even berries could grow on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like a guy's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always had a buzz cut when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would just sit at the barber's with my younger brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they'd just rip my hair off with clippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nickname back then was "Mr. Lady."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you noticed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because I always look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a shocking confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I have to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, your brother plays high school baseball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, his school is a frequent visitor of the Koshien.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'd be proud of him if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm a bit jealous of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-senpai, happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really "oh my."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "oh my"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I meant... What did I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the groups for the field trip are decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this grouping is really weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Ami, Kashii, Aisaka, Kushieda, Takasu, Noto, Haruta and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mixture of nine boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have more girls, I think this is a good grouping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you and Taiga will be{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! But if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not happy about it, go join another group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying, that's why I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell me to shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.28,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to, you can go join{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, even Master Kitamura said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buzz off, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to say such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We need to make a guidebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, each group needs to turn it in by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do something so troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be easier if we worked together on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about my place on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my place is pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't this place a bit over the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much the rent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, do you live next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you live in this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live in an apartment next to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a few examples from previous field trips for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are guides inside these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of a master! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make some black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also brought some madeleines over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, I need to use the computer, where's the outlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you can talk to Kitamura normally now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't really care about it; just go help Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Golgo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I am Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird that there's usable tableware in Taiga's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I came here was in freshman year, so I had the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't been doing anything lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga did this all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason she's able to do it is because you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been here since freshman year?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because of the stuff with her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I wouldn't come here unless I had a reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of failing, so I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't afraid of failing, and you stepped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'd be all right if we just copied this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we copy an Okinawa guide when we're going to a snowy mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, we can't show Yuusaku this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you should worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just making me more curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I guess it must be a big shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a picture, but that magnificent rejection{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid chi-!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Blame the person who brought this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.93,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, tea's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.91,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm kind of looking forward to this field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, it's the last time our class will be doing something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This class is really fun. I'll be lonely without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could stay like this forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could stay like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,staying like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually sorted them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right; I can't stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to confirm Kushieda's true feelings on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ni-Ni-Ni-Nigauri (Bitter melon).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-Ri-Ri-Richiumu Denchi (Lithium battery).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chinome (Blood blister).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meidosan no hesonogoma (A maid's belly button fluff).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandoragora no benishuuga (Mandrake red pickled ginger).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, start with "ga."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ganbaru (Do your best)!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The subject is bitter things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, wasted effort is "bitter" in a sense, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, start with "ru."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ru... Ru... Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.77,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Sukyatto suru Nigamigawa Shibuhiko (Scat-singing Nigamigawa Shibuhiko)!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I have to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.94,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Who the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and deliver those rejected feelings from Christmas to her once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:35.06,Ep Titles 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(323.636364,204)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:35.06,Ep Titles 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs67.5\pos(887.272727,552)}No Matter What
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to confess again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it's for the sake of Taiga who's supporting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really no good; I don't say what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
